creating branch    -- git branch nav-bar 
to switch & create -- git checkout nav-bar
to switch branch   -- git checkout Master(main)
switch & create    -- git switch -c nav-bar
to wsitch branch   -- git switch bugfix
merger the branch  -- git merge nav-bar 
delete barnch      -- git branch -d nav-bar


to list dir       -- ls -la 
